    • Constructor Detail

      • ValidatedCardFactory

        public ValidatedCardFactory(CardType... cardTypes)
        Create a new factory with the given card types.

        Note that the list of card types is in priority order. i.e. When matching, the first CardType matching the card number's pattern will be used.

        Parameters:
        cardTypes - list of card types
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if cardTypes is null
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if cardTypes is empty

      • create

        public ValidatedCard create(CardNumber cardNumber)
        Create a ValidatedCard.

        The first CardType matching the card number's pattern is used, the first match is chosen.

        Parameters:
        cardNumber - card number to match
        Returns:
        a new ValidatedCard instance, or null if a card type matching the card number could not be found
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if cardNumber is null
